strata1.common.datetime
Class DateTime

java.lang.Object
  strata1.common.datetime.DateTime
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<DateTime>, Copyable
public class DateTime
extends Object
implements Copyable, Serializable, Comparable<DateTime>

Provides a simplified abstraction for representing date/time values using Calendar as its internal implementation. DateTime is a Value Object and is therefore immutable.

Author:
Sapientia Systems
See Also:
Calendar, Serialized Form
